      <odd id="aspace_23cc9cd4d7b464da120b0bf585c27846">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 8-C-1 (YRG 8-C-1), Records of organizations open to all Yale alumni.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_21a960d6cbf54bc8f4eea33d137f5068">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were a gift of Corey Alan Friedlander, 2004; Dennis W. Mack, 2010.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_ccbda9b2915875d162adc0b1c489bb83">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the records is restricted. See inventory for details.</p>
         <p>Original born digital files, as well as preservation masters, may not be accessed due to their fragility. Researchers must consult use copies, or if none exist request that they be made. Born digital files cannot be accessed remotely. System requirements include a Manuscripts and Archives computer and file viewing software.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_16ebd65eb3b5e7a3769857337f344d56">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
